Excellent episodes as always. However, the disc holders were loose and a couple of the discs didn't stay when clicked in (a problem with collection 15 as well). In addition, the first disc froze on one of the episodes and had to be cleaned to fix the problem, though it worked well after that.

Other than these slight physical issues, the set is perfect and I look forward to the next one.

I know some folks can't stand English dubs, but you really have to give a round of applause for the dedicated work the English voice actors put into their performances. It's not an easy process, and takes many vigorous hours to bring these beloved characters to life in a new language. My straw hat is off to the folks at Funimation, and I can't wait to Luffy and the gang on their next set of adventures!!
